CREATE FUNCTION dbo.getLatestUserSession(@userId int)
RETURNS TABLE AS
RETURN (
    SELECT TOP 1 * FROM dbo.ShoppingSessions AS C WHERE C.UserId = @userId ORDER BY C.Modified_At DESC
)

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[proc_deleteProductCategory](@productCategoryId int,@actionPeformerId int,@referenceId varchar(250)) 
AS
BEGIN
 INSERT INTO ProductCategories_Archive (

      ,[Desc]
      ,[Created_At]
      ,[Modified_At]
      ,[Action]
      ,[Peformed_At]
      ,[PeformedById]
      ,[Record_Type]
      ,[Reference_Id]
 ) SELECT 
        [Id]
      ,[Name]
      ,[Desc]
      ,[Created_At]
      ,[Modified_At],
    'DELETE' [Action],
    GETDATE() Peformed_At,
    @actionPeformerId,
    'delete' Record_Type
    ,@referenceId  FROM [OnlineShop_v2].[dbo].[ProductCategories] WHERE Id = @productCategoryId
    DELETE FROM ProductCategories WHERE Id = @productCategoryId;
END;

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[proc_deleteShoppingSession](@shoppingSessionId int,@actionPeformerId int,@referenceId varchar(250)) 
AS
BEGIN

INSERT INTO CartItems_Archive (
      [Archive_Id]
      ,[Quantity]
      ,[Created_At]
      ,[Modified_At]
      ,[Product_Id]
      ,[Sub_total]
      ,[ShoppingSession_Id]
      ,[Action]
      ,[Peformed_At]
      ,[PeformedById]
      ,[Record_Type]
      ,[Reference_Id]
)
SELECT 
        [Id]
      ,[Quantity]
      ,[Created_At]
      ,[Modified_At]
      ,[ProductId]
      ,[Sub_total]
      ,[ShoppingSessionId],
        'DELETE' Actions,
        GETDATE() Peformed_At,
        @actionPeformerId,
        'delete' Record_Type
        ,@referenceId 
 FROM  CartItems WHERE ShoppingSessionId = @shoppingSessionId


 INSERT INTO ShoppingSessions_Archive (
      [Archive_Id]
      ,[Total]
      ,[Created_At]
      ,[Modified_At]
      ,[UserId]
      ,[Action]
      ,[Peformed_At]
      ,[PeformedById]
      ,[Record_Type]
      ,[Reference_Id]
 ) SELECT         
        [Id]
      ,[Total]
      ,[Created_At]
      ,[Modified_At]
      ,[UserId],
    'DELETE' Actions,
    GETDATE() Peformed_At,
    @actionPeformerId,
    'delete' Record_Type
    ,@referenceId  from ShoppingSessions WHERE Id = @shoppingSessionId
END;

   DELETE FROM CartItems WHERE ShoppingSessionId = @shoppingSessionId;
   DELETE FROM ShoppingSessions  WHERE Id = @shoppingSessionId;

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[proc_deleteOrderDetail] (@orderDetailId int,@actionPeformerId int,@referenceId varchar(250)) 
AS 
BEGIN
        --Archive all order items
        INSERT INTO OrderItems_Archive (
            [Archive_Id]
            ,[Quantity]
            ,[Created_At]
            ,[Modified_At]
            ,[OrderDetailId]
            ,[ProductId]
            ,[Action]
            ,[Peformed_At]
            ,[PeformedById]
            ,[Record_Type]
            ,[Reference_Id]
        ) 
        SELECT 
            [Id]
            ,[Quantity]
            ,[Created_At]
            ,[Modified_At]
            ,[OrderDetailsId]
            ,[ProductId],
            'DELETE' Actions,
            GETDATE() Peformed_At,
           @actionPeformerId,
            'delete' Record_Type
           ,@referenceId 

        FROM OrderItems WHERE OrderDetailsId = @orderDetailId



        -- Archive all order details
        INSERT INTO OrderDetails_Archive (       
            [Archive_Id]
            ,[Total]
            ,[Created_At]
            ,[Modified_At]
            ,[UserId]
            ,[PaymentDetailsId]
            ,[Status]
            ,[Action]
            ,[Peformed_At]
            ,[PeformedById]
            
            ,[Record_Type]
            ,[Reference_Id]
        )
        SELECT 
                [Id]
            ,[Total]
            ,[Created_At]
            ,[Modified_At]
            ,[UserId]
            ,[PaymentDetailsId]
            ,[Status],
            'DELETE' [Action],
            GETDATE(),
            @actionPeformerId,
            'delete' [Record_Type],
            @referenceId

        FROM OrderDetails WHERE Id = @orderDetailId
      
   DELETE FROM OrderItems WHERE OrderDetailsId = @orderDetailId;
   DELETE FROM OrderDetails WHERE Id = @orderDetailId;
END;

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[proc_deleteUser]
(
    @UserId int,
    @ActionPerformerId int,
    @ReferenceId varchar(250)
)
AS
BEGIN
    -- Archive user payments
    INSERT INTO [OnlineShop_v2].[dbo].[UserPayments_Archive] (
        [Archive_Id],
        [Payment_Type],
        [Card_Holder_Name],
        [Card_Number],
        [CVV],
        [Expiration_Month],
        [Expiration_Year],
        [Created_At],
        [UserId]
    )
    SELECT
        [Id],
        [Payment_Type],
        [Card_Holder_Name],
        [Card_Number],
        [CVV],
        [Expiration_Month],
        [Expiration_Year],
        [Created_At],
        @UserId
    FROM
        [OnlineShop_v2].[dbo].[UserPayments]
    WHERE
        UserId = @UserId;

    -- Archive user addresses
    INSERT INTO [OnlineShop_v2].[dbo].[UserAddresses_Archive] (
        [Archive_Id],
        [Address],
        [Country],
        [City],
        [UserId]
    )
    SELECT
        [Id],
        [Address],
        [Country],
        [City],
        @UserId
    FROM
        [OnlineShop_v2].[dbo].[UserAddresses]
    WHERE
        UserId = @UserId;

    -- Archive password reset tokens
    INSERT INTO [OnlineShop_v2].[dbo].[PasswordResetTokens_Archive] (
        [Archive_Id],
        [Token],
        [Expiration],
        [Created_At],
        [UserId]
    )
    SELECT
        [Id],
        [Token],
        [Expiration],
        [Created_At],
        @UserId
    FROM
        [OnlineShop_v2].[dbo].[PasswordResetTokens]
    WHERE
        UserId = @UserId;

    -- Archive user roles
    INSERT INTO [OnlineShop_v2].[dbo].[UsersRoles_Archive] (
        [Archive_Id],
        [UserId],
        [RoleId]
    )
    SELECT
        [Id],
        [UserId],
        [RoleId]
    FROM
        [OnlineShop_v2].[dbo].[UsersRoles]
    WHERE
        UserId = @UserId;

    -- Archive shopping sessions
    INSERT INTO [OnlineShop_v2].[dbo].[ShoppingSessions_Archive] (
        [Archive_Id],
        [Total],
        [Created_At],
        [Modified_At],
        [UserId]
    )
    SELECT
        [Id],
        [Total],
        [Created_At],
        [Modified_At],
        @UserId
    FROM
        [OnlineShop_v2].[dbo].[ShoppingSessions]
    WHERE
        UserId = @UserId;

    -- Delete user payments
    DELETE FROM [UserPayments] WHERE UserId = @UserId;

    -- Delete user addresses
    DELETE FROM [UserAddresses] WHERE UserId = @UserId;

    -- Delete password reset tokens
    DELETE FROM [PasswordResetTokens] WHERE UserId = @UserId;

    -- Delete user roles
    DELETE FROM [UsersRoles] WHERE UserId = @UserId;

    -- Delete shopping sessions
    DELETE FROM [ShoppingSessions] WHERE UserId = @UserId;
END;
